details.title: Job Description
details.description: • We are looking for a skilled Front End Engineer to join our dynamic team. Your primary responsibility will be to develop user-facing features and ensure a seamless user experience.

details.title: Requirements
details.description:
• Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field.
  • 3-4 years of experience as a Front End Engineer.
  • Proficiency in JavaScript, TypeScript, React.js, and other front-end technologies.
  • Strong understanding of responsive design principles.

details.title: Benefits
details.description:
• Competitive salary and benefits package.
  • Remote work options.
  • Health and wellness programs.
  • Opportunities for career advancement.
